      "html": [
        "<main class=\"page page-01 type-cover\">",
        "  <header class=\"cover-header\">",
        "    <h1 class=\"page-title\">AI的利润表很漂亮<br>但少算了一页</h1>",
        "  </header>",
        "  <section class=\"content-list\">",
        "    <div class=\"content-item\">",
        "      <div class=\"content-tag\">极度利好ai大公司 却让普通人丢掉工作或者极度卷时长</div>",
        "      <p class=\"content-text\">芯片、云和模型订阅变成了巨头收入。但被 AI 影响和替代的裁员岗位，由公众承担。</p>",
        "    </div>",
        "    <div class=\"content-item\">",
        "      <div class=\"content-tag\">训练数据来自每个人 但是ai收益却只被大公司占有</div>",
        "      <p class=\"content-text\">每个用户要付费购买自己数据（点赞 聊天 图片创作 自拍 视频创作等等）训练ai的订阅制会员。这就好比花钱买自己种的粮食一样荒谬</p>",
        "    </div>",
        "  </section>",
        "</main>"
      ],
      "css": [
        "",
        "/* 基本页面设置 */",
        ".page {",
        "  width: 1242px;",
        "  height: 1660px;",
        "  padding: 100px;",
        "  box-sizing: border-box;",
        "  background-color: #F8F8F8;",
        "  font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"PingFang SC\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", sans-serif;",
        "  /* 强制 flex 纵向布局 */",
        "  display: flex;",
        "  flex-direction: column;",
        "  justify-content: space-between; /* 垂直方向上推开内容，实现饱满布局 */",
        "}",
        "",
        "/* 防止单字成行 & 字距 */",
        "* {",
        "  text-wrap: balance;",
        "  letter-spacing: 0;",
        "}",
        "",
        "/* 封面标题 */",
        ".cover-header {",
        "  flex-shrink: 0; /* 防止标题被压缩 */",
        "}",
        "",
        ".page-title {",
        "  font-size: 152px;",
        "  font-weight: 600;",
        "  line-height: 1.25;",
        "  color: #111111;",
        "  margin: 0;",
        "  padding: 0;",
        "}",
        "",
        "/* 内容卡片列表 */",
        ".content-list {",
        "  display: flex;",
        "  flex-direction: column;",
        "  gap: 32px; /* 卡片间距 */",
        "}",
        "",
        ".content-item {",
        "  background-color: #FFFFFF;",
        "  border-radius: 16px;",
        "  padding: 40px 48px;",
        "  box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);",
        "}",
        "",
        "/* 卡片内标签 */",
        ".content-tag {",
        "  display: inline-block;",
        "  margin-bottom: 20px;",
        "  font-size: 34px;",
        "  font-weight: 500;",
        "  padding: 8px 16px;",
        "  color: #E53935;",
        "  background-color: #FFEBEE;",
        "  border-radius: 8px;",
        "}",
        "",
        "/* 卡片内正文 */",
        ".content-text {",
        "  font-size: 40px;",
        "  line-height: 1.6;",
        "  color: #555555;",
        "  margin: 0;",
        "  padding: 0;",
        "}",
        "",
        ".content-text span {",
        "  white-space: nowrap;",
        "}"
      ]
